OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773176766
OL,3,CThousands of top authors publish
OL,4,C'empty' book in AI protest
OL,6,FAround 10,000 authors, including
OL,7,FRichard Osman, Jacqueline Wilson and
OL,8,FMalorie Blackman, have published an
OL,9,F"empty" book to protest AI firms using
OL,10,Ftheir work without permission.
OL,12,FDon't Steal This Book is empty of any
OL,13,Ftext except a list of the names of the
OL,14,Fauthors involved in the project and
OL,15,Fwill be distributed to people at the
OL,16,FLondon Book Fair on Tuesday.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@GO]
