PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773176766
OL,3,CThousands of top authors publish
OL,4,C'empty' book in AI protest
OL,6,F"The book represents the impact on
OL,7,Fauthors' livelihoods and the
OL,8,Fpublishing industry that is expected
OL,9,Fif the government proceeds with plans
OL,10,Fthat would make it easier to train AI
OL,11,Fmodels on copyright-protected work
OL,12,Fwithout a licence," organiser Ed
OL,13,FNewton-Rex said.
OL,15,FAI developers use large volumes of
OL,16,Fonline content to train their models,
OL,17,Fincluding copyright-protected works
OL,18,Fsuch as books, blogs and music.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
