PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773176766
OL,3,CThousands of top authors publish
OL,4,C'empty' book in AI protest
OL,6,FThe book's publication comes a week
OL,7,Fbefore ministers are required to
OL,8,Fpublish a comprehensive economic
OL,9,Fimpact assessment and a progress
OL,10,Freport regarding the interaction
OL,11,Fbetween copyright law and AI.
OL,13,FThe report draws on a consultation
OL,14,Fthat received about 11,500 responses
OL,15,Ffrom stakeholders, including creators
OL,16,Fand rights holders, developers of AI
OL,17,Fmodels and applications, academics and
OL,18,Fresearchers, cultural heritage
OL,19,Forganisations and legal professionals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
