PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773176766
OL,3,CThousands of top authors publish
OL,4,C'empty' book in AI protest
OL,6,FCreatives have expressed concern that
OL,7,Fa loosening of the law could be
OL,8,Fdetrimental to their practices.
OL,10,FThe back cover of the Don't Steal This
OL,11,FBook reads: "The UK government must
OL,12,Fnot legalise book theft to benefit AI
OL,13,Fcompanies."
OL,15,FNewton-Rex, a composer and organiser
OL,16,Fof the campaign, said: "The AI
OL,17,Findustry is built on stolen work - the
OL,18,Flife's work of writers and other
OL,19,Fcreatives, taken without permission or
OL,20,Fpayment.
OL,26,@sD@MOUuD@KO]xD@XOU
