PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773176766
OL,3,CThousands of top authors publish
OL,4,C'empty' book in AI protest
OL,6,FHe said this "was not a victimless
OL,7,Fcrime".
OL,9,F"Generative AI competes with the
OL,10,Fpeople whose work it is trained on,
OL,11,Frobbing them of their livelihoods. The
OL,12,Fgovernment must protect the UK's
OL,13,Fcreatives, and refuse to legalise the
OL,14,Ftheft of creative work by AI
OL,15,Fcompanies."
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
