PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773176766
OL,3,CThousands of top authors publish
OL,4,C'empty' book in AI protest
OL,6,FThere has been growing anger over the
OL,7,Fuse of copyrighted material being used
OL,8,Fby AI, and there have been several
OL,9,Flawsuits from publishers and authors
OL,10,Fglobally. AI company Anthropic agreed
OL,11,Fto payout a $1.5 billion to settle
OL,12,Fwith authors last year.
OL,14,FMalorie Blackman OBE, writer of best
OL,15,Fselling dystopian novel Noughts &
OL,16,FCrosses, is one of the thousands of
OL,17,Fauthors adding her name to the book.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1773176766
OL,3,CThousands of top authors publish
OL,4,C'empty' book in AI protest
OL,6,FBlackman says: "Each book an author
OL,7,Fcreates is the result of time and
OL,8,Feffort, determination and
OL,9,Fperseverance, commitment and craft,
OL,10,Foften honed over many years.
OL,12,F"AI devours the end result, not
OL,13,Frespecting or even acknowledging the
OL,14,Fjourney made to get to that point. It
OL,15,Fis not in any way unreasonable to
OL,16,Fexpect AI companies to pay for the use
OL,17,Fof authors' books."
OL,19,FThis is not the first time we have
OL,20,Fseen creatives produce this kind of
OL,21,Fwork in protest against AI "theft".
OL,26,@nD@POUyD@SO]
