OL,3,CThousands of top authors publish
OL,4,C'empty' book in AI protest
OL,6,FLast year, Newton-Rex also created Is
OL,7,FThis What We Want?, an album by 1,000
OL,8,FUK musicians consisting of recordings
OL,9,Fof empty studios and performance
OL,10,Fspaces.
OL,12,FThe project was supported by household
OL,13,Fnames such Sir Elton John, Kate Bush
OL,14,Fand Paul McCartney.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
